{
  "texts": [
    "The concepts of digital coding and programmable metasurface have matured in recent years.",
    "Programmable metasurface can be efficiently manipulated for different tasks through artificial control.",
    "When AI collides with programmable metasurface, it brings higher adaptability and autonomy to metasurface systems.",
    "Exploring a generalized AI system architecture will be one of the directions to promote the development of programmable metasurface.",
    "In most metasurface optical systems, AI is typically used for backend processing, which leads to a disconnect between system functionality and the metasurface itself, thereby affecting the overall performance of the system."
  ]
}